<p>In the latest development, Paris prosecutors said two people — a 37-year-old man and a 38-year-old woman — were charged and remanded in custody over the daylight theft of the Louvre’s crown jewels, bringing the number of people formally charged to four . The man was charged with participation in theft by an organized gang and criminal conspiracy, while the woman was charged with complicity and criminal conspiracy; both denied involvement, prosecutors added . Investigators have made a series of arrests around Paris this week and said two earlier suspects had been charged after “partially” admitting involvement, as the probe continues into how the museum was breached on Oct. 19 .</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/6zZVfnCCbSK_blCNz0wIydF83bjyUV36alZt7JvTQGYCL9qDadoBEtbQqOEOWgl1hHF3jc1n8IstvH-D8G0jVumFbMiMwZYQfff9lT1GQlo07yhInra2O3U9J7KqaESki5KB0wfU8F-Bg94-5nI2gLgb4-4RoEyw3hSrhfCl6M6MA9NDFVb8yJNf4TCyKLTDLmszH37JZ_8' alt='Police officers in front of the Louvre Museum in Paris, the target of a sensational jewel theft last month.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Forensic evidence: Investigators linked DNA traces found on one of the scooters used to flee the scene to a suspect, aiding identification efforts</li><li>Airport arrest: One suspect, an Algerian national, was arrested at Paris-Charles de Gaulle airport after booking a one-way ticket, officials said</li><li>Prior convictions: Authorities say one of the men previously had theft convictions from 2008 and 2014 and faces another trial in November</li><li>Court procedure: The 38-year-old woman appeared tearful and her hearing was continued behind closed doors at the prosecutor’s request</li><li>Arrest outcomes: Police detained several people in recent days; three of those held this week were released without charges, prosecutors said</li></ul><blockquote>In these serious crime cases, we find that waves of arrests look more like drift nets - Sofia Bougrine</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Paris public prosecutor (Laure Beccuau): The prosecutor&#x27;s office announced preliminary charges for two people arrested this week and said earlier suspects had been charged after partially admitting involvement in the theft. (<a href='https://www.politico.eu/article/2-more-suspects-charged-in-louvre-heist/'>Politico</a>)</li><li>Defense lawyers: Defense lawyers criticized mass detentions as indiscriminate, saying waves of arrests risk catching people who are not involved. (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1952657/38-year-old-woman-charged-in-louvre-heist'>Dawn</a>)</li><li>Suspects (reported): Two of the newly charged suspects denied involvement when they appeared before a magistrate, authorities reported. (<a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/11/1/two-more-suspects-charged-over-louvre-heist'>Al Jazeera</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2025/nov/01/two-more-suspects-charged-over-louvre-heist-taking-total-to-four'>Two more suspects charged over Louvre heist taking total to four</a> - theguardian.com</li><li><a href='https://japantoday.com/category/world/two-more-suspects-including-woman-charged-over-louvre-heist'>Two more suspects including woman charged over Louvre heist</a> - japantoday.com</li><li><a href='https://www.npr.org/2025/11/01/nx-s1-5594194/suspects-charged-louvre-jewel-heist-paris'>2 more suspects are charged in the Louvre jewel heist</a> - npr.org</li><li><a href='https://www.politico.eu/article/2-more-suspects-charged-in-louvre-heist/'>2 more suspects charged in Louvre heist</a> - politico.eu</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/11/1/two-more-suspects-charged-over-louvre-heist'>Two more suspects charged over Louvre heist</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/11/01/world/europe/france-louvre-heist-arrests.html'>Two More Suspects Charged in Louvre Heist Case</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2025/11/01/suspects-louvre-jewe